WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:10.000
Tuymaada-Neft oil company is one of the main enterprises in the oil products market of The Republic of Sakha (Yakutia)

2
00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:14.500
The main activity of the company is the sale of petroleum products in the Republic.

3
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.000
The company has an extensive and reliable distribution network.

4
00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:24.000
Tuymaada-Neft oil company is the only company that imports petroleum products to the Republic along the Northern Sea Route.

5
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:27.500
Also the company imports petroleum products to the Republic by land, water and rail.

6
00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:33.000
Each year the company supplies tens of thousands of tons to the arctic regions of the Republic.

7
00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:39.000
The company has a huge experience of work in a short period of arctic navigation.

8
00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:43.000
Petroleum products are always delivered in full and on time.

9
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:53.500
In 2017 the company built Railroad tank farm complex in the central part of the Republic.

10
00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:59.000
The production capacity of the complex makes it possible to process two thousand tons of petroleum products per day.

11
00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:04.500
This railroad tank farm complex allows the delivery of petroleum products regardless of the navigation period.

12
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:08.500
By connecting the railway with water transport in the middle reaches of the Lena River,

13
00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:15.500
the company created an effective logistics scheme for providing petroleum products to all regions of Yakutia.

14
00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:21.500
Today Tuymaada-Neft oil company has many plans and projects.

15
00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:23.500
These are the construction of new objects,

16
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:26.500
increased profitability and expansion of the existing network of fuel stations,

17
00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:31.500
further development and adjustment of a scheme to provide low-populated areas of the Republic,

18
00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:34.000
the development of new activities.

19
00:01:34.500 --> 00:01:39.500
Already today the company is conducting geological exploration for the extraction of hydrocarbons.

20
00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:48.500
The mission of the company is uninterrupted supply of consumers of the Republic with high-quality and affordable fuel.

21
00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:54.500
And for two decades Tuymaada-Neft oil company despite the difficulties successfully follows the chosen course.